  "detail": "<p>某广东博主揭穿了“清华鹅腿阿姨”用的是“雁鹅”的腿，说在广东“雁鹅”和绿头鸭一样算鸭子，狮头鹅那些贵价的才算真鹅 ，还说在广东鹅和天鹅算是一类动物，大雁和鸭子算一类</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95758bdb81accd94281b3871f26ef8b9_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1412\" data-original-token=\"v2-95758bdb81accd94281b3871f26ef8b9\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95758bdb81accd94281b3871f26ef8b9_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5ac7bd51f3b9071844377d86fd648aa1_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2400\" data-original-token=\"v2-5ac7bd51f3b9071844377d86fd648aa1\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5ac7bd51f3b9071844377d86fd648aa1_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-593a16082d7a568e71258eb6f80b0983_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2400\" data-original-token=\"v2-593a16082d7a568e71258eb6f80b0983\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-593a16082d7a568e71258eb6f80b0983_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f3c5d1df7eb88aec30241fec6825e20_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2400\" data-original-token=\"v2-2f3c5d1df7eb88aec30241fec6825e20\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2f3c5d1df7eb88aec30241fec6825e20_r.jpg\"/></figure><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/631983014/answer/3309625617\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"清华北大的鹅腿阿姨为什么能火起来？\" data-draft-cover=\"\" class=\"internal\">清华北大的鹅腿阿姨为什么能火起来？</a><p>最新进展：“鹅腿阿姨”在一个团购群内发布群公告，称因被举报，“正在配合相关部门工作”，“原材料是鸭腿，以后都会给大家写清楚，介意请勿下单，鹅腿阿姨叫了十几年了，不存在欺诈等行为”。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4746292458e9ea59d783a65906cadf60_1440w.png\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1369\" data-original-token=\"v2-4746292458e9ea59d783a65906cadf60\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4746292458e9ea59d783a65906cadf60_r.jpg\"/></figure><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1867538518401995048%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1867538518401995048&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc\" data-draft-cover=\"\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">baijiahao.baidu.com/s?</span><span class=\"invisible\">id=1867538518401995048&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p></p>",
